<div data-center="opacity: 1" data--500-top="opacity: 0" class="home_content">
  <h1>Welcome to SHOP141</h1><br>
<div data-center="opacity: 1" data--500-top="opacity: 0" class="home_content" style="padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;">
  <p>Shop141 is a marketplace that supplies Amazon products which reflect the mission of charitable organizations across the country. When a user comes to the site and makes a purchase, the charity will receive a percentage of the amount as a donation from Amazon. Shoppers looking to give more can also donate the purchase amount of the product to the charity. We like to call that generous act <em>shopping 141. </em></p>
</div>
</div>

<div id="about" class="bg_parralax" data-type="background" data-speed="17">
  <div data-center="opacity: 1" data--800-top="opacity: 0" class="layer_content1">
    MAKE A DIFFERENCE<br>
    &<br>
    HELP THOSE IN NEED<br>
    WITH EVERY PURCHASE
  </div>
</div>
<div data-center="opacity: 1" data--300-top="opacity: 0" class="about_content">
  <p>We hope that you will find this site worthwhile and continue shopping with us. If you are a registered nonprofit and Shop141 seems like something you want to get into please <a href="mailto:test@gmail.com">let us know</a>.<br></p>
  <div class="quote">
  <em>"Shop141 has allowed our organization to raise adequate funding to provide our kids with an additional meal per day as they engage in a proven curriculum. A HUGE thanks goes out to all the supporters of Shop141." <br><br>
    <span style="padding-left: 600px;">- Compassion International Director</span></em>
  </div>
</div>

